     1	Operation guide: 
     2	    1. add -javaagent:/path/to/ja-netfilter.jar=jetbrains to your vmoptions (manual or auto)
     3	    2. log out of the jb account in the 'Licenses' window
     4	    3. use key on page https://jetbra.in/5d84466e31722979266057664941a71893322460
     5	    4. plugin 'mymap' has been deprecated since version 2022.1
     6	    5. don't care about the activation time, it is a fallback license and will not expire
