    12	
    13	![image-20240222154446368](./assets/image-20240222154446368.png)
    14	
    15	然后在找到你本地 `idea` 的安装目录，比如：D:\common_soft\IntelliJ IDEA 2023.3.4\bin
    16	
    17	再找到 `idea64.exe.vmoptions`
    18	
    19	![image-20240222154652109](./assets/image-20240222154652109.png)
    20	
